    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.26c.20"/>
                
                <fw type="curatorial">20</fw>
                
                <fw type="imprint">
                    <figure>
                        <figDesc>Coat of Arms</figDesc>
                    </figure>
                    
                    <hi rend="caps">SEBAGO SCHOOL</hi>
                        <lb/>
                    5515-<del>5521</del>
                        <lb/>
                    Cates Avenue
                        <lb/>
                    St. Louis 12, Mo.
                        <lb/>
                
                    <hi rend="caps">DIRECTORS
                        <lb/>
                    L. MATTHEWS WERNER
                        <lb/>
                    MARGARET STEELE WERNER</hi>
                </fw>
                
                <opener>
                    <dateline>October 17, 1958</dateline>
                        
                    <address>
                        <addrLine>Dr. John <hi rend="caps">G.</hi> Neihardt</addrLine>
                        <addrLine><hi rend="caps">R.R.</hi> #7</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>Columbia, Missouri</addrLine>
                    </address>
                
                    <salute>Dear John:</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>I have just heard that you are going to be in the city and will address the St. Louis Suburban Teachers Association. We would love to see you while you are in town. If you can stand sleeping on a hide-a-way bed, our guest room is yours.</p>
                
                <p>Margaret and I think of you and yours far oftener than we hear from or see you. If you can visit us, either drop us a note or just walk in the front door. We both send our most affectionate greetings to you and yours.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>Matt</signed>
                </closer>
                
                <fw type="letterhead"><hi rend="caps">CAMP IRONWOOD COMMUNITY FOR BOYS AND GIRLS, AT HARRISON, MAINE, IS THE SEABAGO EASTERN CAMP</hi></fw>
                
            </div1>
        </body>
        
